rd. Ob für das erste Referat, die Hausarbeit oder die Bachelor- oder Masterarbeit: hiermit steht Ihnen ein kompetenter Leitfaden für die erfolgreiche altertumswissenschaftliche Recherche zur Verfügung.  aThe volume Erfolgreich recherchieren – Altertumswissenschaften und Archäologie provides a comprehensive overview of digital information and research resources as well as sources to the most important sub-areas of the Classial Studies and Archaeology, especially of Pre- and Early History and Archaeology of Roman Provinces. Key research tools and strategies for conducting a successful literature search will be presented.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aArchaeologyxResearchxMethodology. 0aCivilization, ClassicalxInformation resources. 0aCivilization, ClassicalxResearchxMethodology. 4aAltertumswissenschaft. 4aClassical Studies, Archaeology. 4aInformation literacy. 4aInformationskompetenz. 4aInformationsressourcen. 4aRecherche. 4aStudium. 4ainformation resources. 4aresearch. 4astudy. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Library & Information Science / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Library and Information Science 2016z9783110485240oZDB-23-DGB0 cEPUBz97831103962320 cprintz978311029902140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311029903840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110299038423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110299038.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LB  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGBb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016